## Animation & Transition Enhancement

### Performance-Optimized Animations
Use CSS transforms and opacity for smooth animations:

```css
/* Smooth transitions using CSS custom properties */
.component {
  transition: all 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  will-change: transform, opacity;
}

.component:hover {
  transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.02);
  opacity: 0.95;
}

/* Loading animations */
@keyframes pulse {
  0%, 100% {
    opacity: 1;
  }
  50% {
    opacity: 0.5;
  }
}

.loading {
  animation: pulse 2s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1) infinite;
}

/* Fade in animation */
@keyframes fadeIn {
  from {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(10px);
  }
  to {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
}

.fade-in {
  animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease-out forwards;
}
```

### Micro-interactions
Add subtle micro-interactions for better UX:

```css
/* Button micro-interactions */
.button {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.button::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  width: 0;
  height: 0;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  border-radius: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  transition: width 0.3s ease, height 0.3s ease;
}

.button:active::before {
  width: 200px;
  height: 200px;
}

/* Card hover effects */
.card {
  transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
}

.card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
}

/* Input focus effects */
.input {
  transition: border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
}

.input:focus {
  border-color: var(--brand-red-500);
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(244, 63, 94, 0.1);
}
