## Design System Integration

### Component Variant System
```jsx
// Unified component variant system
const createVariantClasses = (component, variant, size) => {
  const baseClasses = {
    button: 'inline-flex items-center justify-center font-medium rounded-md transition-all',
    card: 'rounded-lg overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300',
    badge: 'inline-flex items-center font-medium rounded-full'
  };
  
  const variantClasses = {
    button: {
      primary: 'bg-[var(--brand-red-600)] text-white hover:bg-[var(--brand-red-700)]',
      secondary: 'bg-[var(--brand-blue-500)] text-white hover:bg-[var(--brand-blue-600)]',
      outline: 'bg-transparent border border-[var(--border-color)] hover:bg-[var(--bg-secondary)]'
    },
    card: {
      default: 'bg-[var(--bg-primary)] border border-[var(--border-color)] shadow-[var(--shadow-sm)]',
      elevated: 'bg-[var(--bg-primary)] border border-[var(--border-color)] shadow-[var(--shadow-md)]'
    }
  };
  
  const sizeClasses = {
    button: {
      sm: 'px-[var(--spacing-3)] py-[var(--spacing-1.5)] text-[var(--text-sm)]',
      md: 'px-[var(--spacing-4)] py-[var(--spacing-2)] text-[var(--text-base)]',
      lg: 'px-[var(--spacing-5)] py-[var(--spacing-2.5)] text-[var(--text-lg)]'
    }
  };
  
  return cn(
    baseClasses[component],
    variantClasses[component]?.[variant] || '',
    sizeClasses[component]?.[size] || ''
  );
};
```

This enhanced UI/UX system maintains the exact color schemes and design language while implementing modern, high-performance CSS techniques that improve user experience and maintainability.
